description: Try our easy to follow Baby Zucchinis With Fish & Couscous recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Baby Zucchinis With Fish & Couscous Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 large handful fresh flat-leaf parsley (finely chopped)
550g white fish (such as haddock, cut into chunky bite-sized pieces)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat the oven to 150°C. Put 2 tablespoons of the oil in a bowl, add the zucchinis, and mix well until evenly coated. Fry in a hot grill pan for 2 minutes on each side, then put to one side. You may need to do this in batches.

Add the rest of the oil to the bowl, together with the lime juice and zest, tomato purée, five-spice powder, cayenne, paprika, black pepper, parsley, and garlic. Mix well, then add the fish, stock, couscous, and zucchinis and combine carefully.
Transfer to a flameproof dish and cover with foil. Cook in the oven for 20 minutes, then stir well, and serve.
